lead_paragraph: DeMar DeRozan scored 27 points, Kyle Lowry added 22 and Jonas Valanciunas led a strong defensive effort that carried the Toronto Raptors to a 99-95 victory over the Memphis Grizzlies on Friday night at FedExForum.

headline.print_headline: Raptors Edge Weakened Grizzlies in Memphis
